# Nexo MCP / Developer Access
# ============================
# Your developer key identifies you (the person).
# Get it from: Nexo Dashboard → Profile → Developer Access
# Format: nexo_uak_...
# Keys are per-environment — a staging key does not work on production.
NEXO_DEVELOPER_KEY=

# Nexo instance URL (no trailing slash)
# Defaults to production if not set.
#   Production: https://nexo.luzia.com
#   Staging:    https://staging.nexo.luzia.com
#   Local:      http://localhost:8000
# NEXO_BASE_URL=https://nexo.luzia.com

# ---
# For webhook example services, see examples/.env.example
